Blokus Duo
==========

Setup
-----

    $ make -C cgi
    $ ruby blokus_server.rb

Then access http://localhost:8880/ in your browser.


How to Play
-----------

- Select computer level and color (violet is the first move) to start a game.
- Drag your piece and place it on the board.
- Double click to flip a piece.
- Use mouse wheel or Shift+Click to rotate a piece.

See http://blokus.com/pdf/notice-blokus-duo-en.pdf for the rules of the game.
